================================================================================
                        🔧 TROUBLESHOOTING
================================================================================

"App won't load"
→ Make sure all 8 files are in the same folder
→ Make sure they're extracted (not in a zip)
→ Try opening from a local server (see SETUP_GUIDE.md)

"API key error"
→ Make sure you copied the entire key
→ Check at https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
→ Try a fresh API key

"Chat not working"
→ Check if API key is set (Settings > API Key field)
→ Check browser console (F12) for errors
→ Make sure internet is connected

"Need help?"
→ Check SETUP_GUIDE.md troubleshooting section
→ Read error messages carefully (F12 console)
→ Check README.md FAQ

